hamdi-saidani/"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://stewartrecipes.com/easy-basic-pancakes-recipe/#faq-question-1755543114464","position":1,"url":"https://stewartrecipes.com/easy-basic-pancakes-recipe/#faq-question-1755543114464","name":"Can I omit the sugar?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It's not recommended. The small amount of sugar in the recipe contributes to the browning and the tender texture of the pancakes.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://stewartrecipes.com/easy-basic-pancakes-recipe/#faq-question-1755543115438","position":2,"url":"https://stewartrecipes.com/easy-basic-pancakes-recipe/#faq-question-1755543115438","name":"Can I use water or dairy-free milk?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. You can replace the dairy milk with an equal amount of water or your favorite unsweetened dairy-free milk, like almond or oat milk. The pancakes will be slightly less rich.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://stewartrecipes.com/easy-basic-pancakes-recipe/#faq-question-1755543115997","position":3,"url":"https://stewartrecipes.com/easy-basic-pancakes-recipe/#faq-question-1755543115997","name":"Can I use a different flour?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"For a healthier option, you can swap half of the all-purpose flour for whole-wheat flour. For a gluten-free version, use a 1-to-1 gluten-free all-purpose flour blend.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"}]}</script>
